                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/gallery&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>3. And finally defining <code>gallery#second</code> in css file with <code>overflow-x: scroll;</code> :</p>
<pre class="lang-css prettyprint-override"><code>gallery
        {
            display: flex;
            /*flex-wrap: wrap;*/
            justify-content: flex-start;
            background-color: #5B7A8C;
            background-image: url(&quot;KBHassets/images/KBH/KBHtexture.png&quot;);
        }

gallery#second
        {
            overflow-x: scroll;
        }
</code></pre>
<p>4. If you want the size of items to be fixed, turn the <code>width</code> definition into <code>min-width</code> :</p>
<pre class="lang-css prettyprint-override"><code>div.gallery-item
        {
            min-width: 370px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
</code></pre>
