Q: Architecture - Conditional Statement &amp; Processing A: <p>What about this:</p>
<pre><code>string message = buildMessage(...)

func buildMessage(...)
    if (... /* specific msg condition */)
        // build specific message
        ...
        return message
    }
    // build generic message
    ...
    return message
    // or
    // return buildGenericMessage(...)
}
</code></pre>
